---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import FormHandler from '../../components/FormHandler.astro';
import { IMAGES, SHOW_IMAGE_LABELS } from '../../data/images';
---

<BaseLayout theme="diy" title="How You Can Add $50,000 to Your Florida Home's Sale Price | Blackburn Realty Group" description="The 24-page Florida pre-sale improvement playbook. Real ROI data, value-destroying renovations, and the $40,000 mistakes most owners make.">

<div class="breadcrumb">
  <div class="breadcrumb-inner">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <span class="breadcrumb-sep">/</span>
    <span>DIY Guides</span>
    <span class="breadcrumb-sep">/</span>
    <span>Diy Guide #02</span>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="diy-hero reveal" style={`--diy-hero-img: url('${IMAGES.diyImprove.src}')`}>
  <div class="diy-hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="diy-hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="diy-hero-left">
    <p class="diy-hero-eyebrow">DIY Guide #02</p>
    <h1 class="diy-hero-title">How You Can Add <em>$50,000</em> to Your Florida Home's Sale Price for Under $5,000.</h1>
    <p class="diy-hero-sub">A comprehensive pre-sale improvement playbook for Florida homeowners — what actually adds value, what costs you money, and the renovations that destroy resale.</p>
    <div class="diy-hero-meta">
      <span class="meta-item"><strong>24</strong>Pages</span>
      <span class="meta-item"><strong>30</strong>Min Read</span>
      <span class="meta-item"><strong>FREE</strong>No Obligation</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="diy-hero-right">
    <div class="pdf-mockup">
      <div class="mockup-brand">Blackburn Realty Group</div>
      <div class="mockup-eyebrow">DIY Guide 02 of 04</div>
      <div class="mockup-title">How You Can Add <em>$50,000 to Your Sale Price</em></div>
      <div class="mockup-sub">A Florida-specific pre-sale improvement playbook &mdash; ROI by category, hidden traps, and renovation disasters.</div>
      <div class="mockup-toc-title">Inside the Guide</div>
      <div class="mockup-toc-item"><span>01. The 14 renovations that destroy value</span><span>06</span></div><div class="mockup-toc-item"><span>02. Real Florida ROI math</span><span>09</span></div><div class="mockup-toc-item"><span>03. The 7-day curb appeal sprint</span><span>12</span></div><div class="mockup-toc-item"><span>04. Kitchen: $800 vs $40,000</span><span>14</span></div><div class="mockup-toc-item"><span>05. The $400 bathroom transformation</span><span>17</span></div><div class="mockup-toc-item"><span>06. Roof &amp; HVAC: Florida realities</span><span>19</span></div><div class="mockup-toc-item"><span>07. Paint, color, and staging</span><span>21</span></div><div class="mockup-toc-item"><span>08. If you are renovating remotely</span><span>23</span></div>
      <div class="mockup-page-num">A Florida Owner's Guide</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {SHOW_IMAGE_LABELS && !IMAGES.diyImprove.team && (
    <div class="diy-hero-imglabel">Image · {IMAGES.diyImprove.intent}</div>
  )}
</section>

<section class="reframe-section">
  <p class="reframe-label">First, an honest word</p>
  <h2 class="reframe-title">An honest word <em>before you swing a hammer.</em></h2>
  <p class="reframe-body">You opened this guide because the title promised you a $50,000 lift on your sale price for $5,000 in investment. That headline is real — it happens. But it is not the most important reason this guide exists.</p>
  <div class="reframe-pull">The more important reason: most homeowners about to sell will spend $8,000-$45,000 on improvements that will not return a single dollar at closing.</div>
  <p class="reframe-body">Some renovations will actively reduce your sale price. Others will simply break even — wasting both money and time. The difference between the right improvements and the wrong ones cannot be intuited from HGTV, Pinterest, or your neighbor's contractor recommendation. This guide prevents the most common, most expensive, most regretted pre-sale renovation mistakes in the Florida market.</p>
</section>

<section class="benefits-section">
  <p class="benefits-label">Inside the 24 pages</p>
  <h2 class="benefits-title">What you will <em>actually face.</em></h2>
  <p class="benefits-sub">The full Florida pre-sale renovation landscape — including the $34,000 black-cabinet kitchen disaster, the $52,000 over-improvement trap, and the contractor who took $48,000 and disappeared.</p>
  <div class="benefits-grid"><div class="benefit-cell"><div class="benefit-num">01</div><div class="benefit-text">The 14 renovations that actively destroy Florida home value — including the 'modernization' choices currently being marketed to sellers</div></div><div class="benefit-cell"><div class="benefit-num">02</div><div class="benefit-text">Florida ROI data from actual 2024-2026 closings across 15 improvement categories — separating the 130%+ returns from the negative-ROI traps</div></div><div class="benefit-cell"><div class="benefit-num">03</div><div class="benefit-text">The 7-day curb appeal sprint that increases showings 30-40% for under $1,200 — the one DIY-friendly improvement worth attempting alone</div></div><div class="benefit-cell"><div class="benefit-num">04</div><div class="benefit-text">The kitchen decision framework: when an $800 refresh outperforms a $40,000 renovation, and the over-improvement trap that wastes $20,000+</div></div><div class="benefit-cell"><div class="benefit-num">05</div><div class="benefit-text">The $400 bathroom transformation method professional stagers use — and why $25,000 bathroom renovations rarely return their cost</div></div><div class="benefit-cell"><div class="benefit-num">06</div><div class="benefit-text">Florida's roof age underwriting rules and the HVAC requirements that affect every buyer's financing — the two improvements that consistently pay back</div></div><div class="benefit-cell"><div class="benefit-num">07</div><div class="benefit-text">The 2026 Florida-buyer paint palette with specific brand colors — and the dated trends actively reducing your sale price right now</div></div><div class="benefit-cell"><div class="benefit-num">08</div><div class="benefit-text">Three case studies of remote-renovation disasters by international sellers — including the Buenos Aires owner who lost $96,000 net to a vanished contractor</div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="intl-warning">
  <p class="intl-label">If you are buying from abroad</p>
  <p class="intl-body">If you are managing pre-sale renovations on a Florida property from another country, the risk profile of every recommendation in this guide multiplies. Wrong contractors, abandoned jobs, mechanic's liens, code violations, and HOA denials are common outcomes of remote-managed Florida renovations. If you cannot be physically present, do not start the project — or hire a local broker to manage the entire renovation cycle on your behalf.</p>
</div>

<section class="form-section">
  <div class="form-card" data-ghl-form data-source="diy-improve">
    <p class="form-card-eyebrow">Get the Free Guide</p>
    <h2 class="form-card-title">Download the <em>full 24-page PDF.</em></h2>
    <p class="form-card-sub">Sent instantly to your inbox. We will follow up once after a week to ask if you have questions. That's it.</p>

    <div class="form-row">
      <div class="form-field">
        <label class="form-label">First Name</label>
        <input type="text" name="first_name" class="form-input" placeholder="Jane" />
      </div>
      <div class="form-field">
        <label class="form-label">Last Name</label>
        <input type="text" name="last_name" class="form-input" placeholder="Doe" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-row">
      <div class="form-field">
        <label class="form-label">Email Address</label>
        <input type="email" name="email" class="form-input" placeholder="you@email.com" />
      </div>
      <div class="form-field">
        <label class="form-label">Phone</label>
        <input type="tel" name="phone" class="form-input" placeholder="(305) 555-0123" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-field">
      <label class="form-label">Preferred Language</label>
      <select name="language" class="form-select">
        <option>English</option>
        <option>Spanish / Espanol</option>
        <option>Portuguese / Portugues</option>
        <option>French / Francais</option>
        <option>Mandarin</option>
        <option>Russian</option>
        <option>Arabic</option>
        <option>Other / Specify in follow-up</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <button class="btn-primary form-submit ghl-submit">Send Me the Guide</button>
    <p class="form-privacy">Your info stays private &middot; Used only to deliver this guide &middot; Unsubscribe any time</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="author-section">
  <div class="author-card">
    <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1181686/pexels-photo-1181686.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=300" alt="Olga Blackburn" class="author-photo" />
    <div>
      <div class="author-byline">Author &middot; Blackburn Realty Group</div>
      <div class="author-name">Olga Blackburn</div>
      <p class="author-bio">Licensed Florida real estate broker. Founder of Blackburn Realty Group, a division of The Keyes Company. Most renovation advice online is written by contractors with something to sell. This guide is written by a broker who watches what actually moves a Florida home in 2026 — and what doesn't.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="cta-strip-inner">
    <p class="cta-strip-eyebrow">Want the Real Conversation?</p>
    <h2 class="cta-strip-headline">Skip the guide. <em>Talk to a person.</em></h2>
    <p class="cta-strip-body">If reading 22 pages of Florida real estate complexity is not how you want to spend your week, book a free 30-minute call instead. We will give you the answers specific to your situation, in your language, with no obligation.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/tools/consultation/" class="btn-primary">Book a Consultation</a>
      <a href="/ladies/" class="btn-secondary">Find an Agent</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="mobile-sticky">
  <a href="/ladies/" class="mobile-sticky-btn">Find My Agent</a>
  <a href="/tools/preapproval/" class="mobile-sticky-btn">Get Pre-Approved</a>
  <a href="/tools/homevalue/" class="mobile-sticky-btn">Home Value</a>
</div>


<script is:inline>
  (function () {
    var els = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
    if (!('IntersectionObserver' in window)) { els.forEach(function (e) { e.classList.add('is-in'); }); return; }
    var io = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
      entries.forEach(function (entry) {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) { entry.target.classList.add('is-in'); io.unobserve(entry.target); }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.1, rootMargin: '0px 0px -6% 0px' });
    els.forEach(function (e) { io.observe(e); });
  })();
</script>

<FormHandler />

</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
    .nav-item > a:hover { color: var(--white); }
    
    .nav-dropdown a:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .nav-dropdown a:hover { color: var(--white); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); padding-left: 30px; }
    .nav-dropdown a.ladies { border-left: 2px solid var(--pink); }
    .nav-dropdown a.guys { border-left: 2px solid var(--turquoise); }
    .nav-dropdown a.ladies:hover { color: var(--pink); }
    .nav-dropdown a.guys:hover { color: var(--turquoise); }

    /* breadcrumb */

    .breadcrumb-inner a:hover { color: var(--theme); }

    /* page hero shared */
    .page-hero {
      padding: 60px 52px 80px;
      max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .page-eyebrow {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.4em; color: var(--theme);
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .page-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em; color: var(--white);
      line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .page-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--theme); }
    .page-sub {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-style: italic; font-weight: 300;
      font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2.2vw, 1.5rem);
      color: var(--silver); max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* sections */
    .section {
      padding: 80px 52px;
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .section-wide { max-width: 1400px; }
    .section h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.2vw, 3.2rem);
      color: var(--white); line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 28px;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    .section h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--theme); }
    .section h3 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .section-label {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.38em; color: var(--theme);
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .section p {
      font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.95; color: var(--silver-mid);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .section p.lead {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-style: italic; font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--silver-light);
      line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .section-rule {
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), transparent);
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* buttons */

    /* final cta strip */

    .cta-strip-headline em { font-style: italic; color: var(--theme); }

    /* footer */

    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--silver-light); }

    /* mobile sticky */
    .mobile-sticky {
      display: none;
      position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 90;
      background: rgba(6,6,6,0.97);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      padding: 12px 16px; gap: 8px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }
    .mobile-sticky-btn {
      flex: 1;
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
      text-align: center; text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 8px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      color: var(--silver-light);
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .mobile-sticky-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }

    /* mobile */
    @media (max-width: 860px) {

      .mobile-sticky { display: flex; }
      
      .page-hero { padding: 40px 22px 50px; }
      .section { padding: 60px 22px; }

    }

    .diy-hero {
      padding: 100px 52px 60px;
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 80px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .diy-hero-left { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
    .diy-hero-eyebrow {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.4em; color: var(--theme);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .diy-hero-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.5vw, 3.6rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.005em; color: var(--white);
      line-height: 1.1;
    }
    .diy-hero-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--theme); }
    .diy-hero-sub {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-style: italic; font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--silver); line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .meta-item {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--silver-dark);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .meta-item strong { color: var(--white); margin-right: 6px; font-weight: 600; }

    .diy-hero-right {
      position: relative;
      display: flex; justify-content: center;
    }
    .pdf-mockup {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 420px;
      aspect-ratio: 8.5/11;
      background: #fafaf7;
      box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      padding: 48px 40px;
      transform: rotate(-2deg);
      transition: transform 0.4s;
    }
    .pdf-mockup:hover { transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1.03); }
    .pdf-mockup::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 20px; left: -16px; bottom: 20px;
      width: 8px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0,0,0,0.3), transparent);
    }
    .mockup-brand {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em; color: #060606;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding-bottom: 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #d4d4d4;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .mockup-eyebrow {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.62rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.32em; color: #888;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .mockup-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.55rem;
      color: #060606; line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .mockup-title em { font-style: italic; }
    .mockup-sub {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-style: italic; font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 0.92rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }
    .mockup-toc-title {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em; color: #999;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .mockup-toc-item {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
      font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.7rem; color: #333;
      padding: 5px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px dotted #ccc;
    }
    .mockup-page-num {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 24px; right: 40px;
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: #888; text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* Reframe callout - the bait and switch */
    .reframe-section {
      max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 70px 52px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }
    .reframe-label {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.4em; color: var(--theme);
      text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .reframe-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
      color: var(--white); text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.25; margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .reframe-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--theme); }
    .reframe-body em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--white);
    }
    .reframe-pull {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-style: italic; font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      line-height: 1.45; color: var(--white);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px 40px;
      margin: 32px 0;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--theme);
      background: rgba(232,232,232,0.03);
    }

    /* What's inside - now showing complexity */
    .benefits-section {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 80px 52px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }
    .benefits-label {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.4em; color: var(--theme);
      text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .benefits-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.2vw, 2.8rem);
      color: var(--white); text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .benefits-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--theme); }
    .benefits-sub {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-style: italic; font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--silver);
      text-align: center; max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto 56px;
    }
    .benefits-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    .benefit-cell {
      padding: 32px 36px;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .benefit-num {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--theme); line-height: 1;
      min-width: 36px;
    }
    .benefit-text {
      font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.98rem;
      color: var(--silver-light); line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* International warning callout */
    .intl-warning {
      max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 36px 44px;
      background: var(--near-black);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--theme);
      margin-bottom: 80px;
    }
    .intl-label {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.66rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.32em; color: var(--theme);
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    /* Form section */
    .form-section {
      max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 80px 52px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }
    .form-card {
      background: var(--near-black);
      padding: 56px 48px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }
    .form-card-eyebrow {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.32em; color: var(--theme);
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .form-card-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: 2rem;
      color: var(--white); line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 14px; text-align: center;
    }
    .form-card-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--theme); }
    .form-card-sub {
      font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: 0.92rem;
      color: var(--silver-dark); line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 36px; text-align: center;
